Class PolicyConditionBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.databuilder.DataBuilder<T,B>
      • gw.api.builder.ClauseBuilder<PolicyCondition,PolicyConditionBuilder,ConditionPattern>
        • gw.api.builder.PolicyConditionBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueGenerator<PolicyCondition>

    public class PolicyConditionBuilder
extends ClauseBuilder<PolicyCondition,PolicyConditionBuilder,ConditionPattern>
    Builder for PolicyCondition (a type of Clause). This builder can only be used in the context of a Coverable, so the common usage would look like 
       ...
   new PersonalAutoLineBuilder().withCondition(new PolicyConditionBuilder()...)
   ...
